Another Sarah fucking Bernhardt?

25:05.138 --> 25:06.707
Well, I was much better than her.

25:06.740 --> 25:08.408
Ooh! Oh!

25:08.441 --> 25:11.278
Modest with it.

25:11.311 --> 25:15.649
I grew up in an experimental theater.
Ah! Suck it and see.

25:15.683 --> 25:20.854
There was a director, the heart
