25:45.412 --> 25:47.581
So, is that why you're here?

25:50.050 --> 25:51.284
I don't know what you mean.

25:55.022 --> 25:58.726
"Will you play upon this pipe?"
Recognize it?

25:58.759 --> 26:01.461
Act Three, Scene Two.
But I don't know it in English.

26:01.494 --> 26:03.797
Oh! Come on, Dorottya.

26:03.831 --> 26:06.133
You're not gonna pass up
the chance to play Guildenstern

26:06.166 --> 26:09.670
opposite to
Sir Michael Gifford's Hamlet?

26:09.703 --> 26:11.071
"Will you play upon this pipe?"

26:12.773 --> 26:15.776
"My Lord, I cannot."
"I pray you."

26:15.809 --> 26:19.412
"Believe me, I cannot."
"I do beseech you."

26:19.446 --> 26:21.148
"I know no touch of it, my Lord."

26:21.181 --> 26:23.517
