a Lifetime Achievement Award.

28:10.357 --> 28:11.792
About fucking time.

28:12.993 --> 28:14.928
What? They run out of pygmies?

28:14.962 --> 28:16.664
TV stars and second-raters?

28:19.032 --> 28:22.335
- Do I have to pay?
- Of course you don't.

28:22.369 --> 28:24.371
I said that you'd be very honored,

28:24.404 --> 28:26.373
and I would accept the award
on your behalf.

28:26.406 --> 28:27.541
Mmm...

28:27.575 --> 28:29.009
Just like your mother.

28:30.611 --> 28:33.446
Not only my money,
you want my glory, too.

28:35.883 --> 28:38.051
God. What a monster you've become.

28:39.853 --> 28:41.454
