28:48.562 --> 28:52.232
And find Joseph, will you?
I need a word.

29:08.649 --> 29:10.317
Do you think
they're all the same age?

29:10.350 --> 29:12.185
I haven't the foggiest idea.

29:12.219 --> 29:15.989
