ever really very funny.

30:06.840 --> 30:09.342
Can I ask you a personal question?

30:10.844 --> 30:12.212
Were you and him ever...

30:14.447 --> 30:17.150
It was ages ago.

30:17.184 --> 30:19.653
He didn't want to get a divorce,

30:19.687 --> 30:22.222
I wanted to kill myself.

30:22.255 --> 30:25.158
I didn't, of course.
People generally don't.

30:25.192 --> 30:26.259
Some do.

30:27.861 --> 30:30.798
Particularly the very young.

30:30.831 --> 30:31.603
They're so impatient.

30:31.605 --> 30:33.367
They're incapable of
waiting for anything.

30:33.400 --> 30:34.902
Even death.

30:38.238 --> 30:40.641
Drink up. You've got a train to catch.

30:43.877 --> 30:46.647
- You wanted to see me, sir?
- Yes, Joseph.

30:46.680 --> 30:48.181
Come in.
Close the door.

30:50.217 --> 30:53.353
- You're looking a bit scruffy.
- I've been gardening, sir.

30:53.386 --> 30:58.859
Oh! Yes, of course.
"Thrift, thrift, Horatio!"

30:58.892 --> 31:01.294
- Sit down.
- I...

31:02.563 --> 31:04.464
Sit! Mmm!

31:04.497 --> 31:08.268
- Tea? Do you like muffins?
- No, thank you, sir.

31:09.970 --> 31:11.404
How long have we known
each other, Joseph?

31:13.674 --> 31:16.009
Ooh! Well, over 40 years, sir.

31:16.043 --> 31:17.911
We've always got along
pretty well, haven't we?

31:17.945 --> 31:20.113
