- Sir Michael.

31:42.069 --> 31:43.737
The girl, Joseph.

31:44.572 --> 31:47.107
Don't piss about.

31:47.140 --> 31:50.978
Well, I just thought
you'd both be well suited.

31:52.312 --> 31:54.582
You must admit, she's perked you up.

31:54.615 --> 31:57.651
And all that Shakespeare,
she speaks it, too.

31:58.952 --> 32:00.954
So we speak the same language, yeah?

32:00.988 --> 32:02.956
Yes, sir, that's about it.

32:03.657 --> 32:04.725
Hmm...

32:05.392 --> 32:06.660
I'll...

32:11.131 --> 32:12.533
Joseph.

32:12.566 --> 32:16.103
