33:16.864 --> 33:18.566
- Much improvement since last time.
- Thank you.

33:20.167 --> 33:21.835
Next.

33:21.869 --> 33:24.037
Dorottya Horvat.

33:24.071 --> 33:25.138
You're next.

33:25.939 --> 33:27.508
Good luck.

33:32.646 --> 33:33.981
How are you?

33:34.014 --> 33:34.731
