You let her go.

36:17.410 --> 36:20.180
Look.
Oh, it's sweet.

36:20.213 --> 36:21.849
Remind you of anyone?

36:24.317 --> 36:26.353
I'm glad you like her.

36:26.386 --> 36:29.456
She's the first one you don't
seem to mind having around.

36:29.489 --> 36:30.958
Milly.

36:30.991 --> 36:32.325
Don't tell me you're jealous.

36:32.359 --> 36:34.762
No, of course I'm not.
I just...

36:34.795 --> 36:38.666
