36:38.699 --> 36:40.534
She has fire in her belly.

36:41.902 --> 36:45.038
She reminds me of myself at that age.

36:45.072 --> 36:48.676
A mixture of innocence,
hunger, and ruthlessness.

36:50.043 --> 36:52.580
